[BUGFIX][ISU2024082885007] Modify platform module stop service disable service first and then stop service

Reviewer:
	liwenlong
Root cause:
	In reboot process, systemd-shutdown will stop platform-module-baidu service, stop command spend much time, cause service not disable successfuly
Solution:
	1. After Execstop platform-module-baidu.service, First to systemctl disable xxx.service qucikly, Second systemctl stop xxx.service
